  "x-artifact": {
    "kind": "mcp-server-definition",
    "designFirst": true,
    "deployed": false,
    "note": "Design-first artifact only \u2014 describes the MCP tool surface, not a running server. Tool input/output schemas $ref the same object schemas as the OpenAPI; each tool maps to an OpenAPI operationId. Surfaces DCAS's open civil-service reference data (job postings, titles, eligible lists, exam schedule, buildings, fleet) and adds register_for_exam \u2014 the net-new write workflow locked today inside the OASys / City Jobs application layer.",
